text: Rainbow’s hanging in the blue sky. I open my eyes, seeing the sunlight where's the way to the Holy Land.
I’m going fast like the wind. Hometown is so far away. It is in my heart. it is on my mind.
You are the only hope of me. I am longing to see you again.
I wish I can just sit by your side, waiting for the sunrise.
Show you the love tattoo on my back. I see crystal tears are on your face.
Do you know how brave I’m lonely on my way?
